n maslinik, koji se prostire na površini od 13.000 m2 i broji skoro 1000 stabala maslina.\",\"_bottom_text\":\"field_67ea882efb29a\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/block-image-accordion {\"name\":\"acf/block-image-accordion\",\"data\":{\"visibility_checkin_section_visibility\":\"0\",\"_visibility_checkin_section_visibility\":\"field_67ea873076702\",\"visibility_accordion_section_visibility\":\"0\",\"_visibility_accordion_section_visibility\":\"field_67ea876d76703\",\"visibility_list_section_visibility\":\"0\",\"_visibility_list_section_visibility\":\"field_67ea88fefb2a1\",\"visibility\":\"\",\"_visibility\":\"field_67ea87cd76705\",\"title\":\"\",\"_title\":\"field_67ea6a9caef00\",\"subtitle\":\"\",\"_subtitle\":\"field_67ea6aa6aef01\",\"image\":\"\",\"_image\":\"field_67ea6a87aeeff\",\"bottom_title\":\"\",\"_bottom_title\":\"field_67ea884efb29b\",\"bottom_text\":\"Na području Zračne luke Split nalazi se kamena srednjovjekovna crkvica “Sv. Bare“, zaštitnika Zračne luke Split. Kamena crkvica datira s kraja 13. i početka 14. stoljeća, a nalazi se na brdu u blizini maslinika.\",\"_bottom_text\":\"field_67ea882efb29a\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/block-image-accordion {\"name\":\"acf/block-image-accordion\",\"data\":{\"visibility_checkin_section_visibility\":\"0\",\"_visibility_checkin_section_visibility\":\"field_67ea873076702\",\"visibility_accordion_section_visibility\":\"0\",\"_visibility_accordion_section_visibility\":\"field_67ea876d76703\",\"visibility_list_section_visibility\":\"0\",\"_visibility_list_section_visibility\":\"field_67ea88fefb2a1\",\"visibility\":\"\",\"_visibility\":\"field_67ea87cd76705\",\"title\":\"\",\"_title\":\"field_67ea6a9caef00\",\"subtitle\":\"\",\"_subtitle\":\"field_67ea6aa6aef01\",\"image\":\"\",\"_image\":\"field_67ea6a87aeeff\",\"bottom_title\":\"\",\"_bottom_title\":\"field_67ea884efb29b\",\"bottom_text\":\"U okviru upravljanja zaštite okoliša vodi se računa o načinu gospodarenja otpadom. Izrađen je interni elaborat – “Plan o gospodarenju otpadom Zračne luke Split“. Navedenim dokumentom je definirana organizacijska struktura i tehničko-tehnološki procesi postupanja s otpadom. Svi procesi se obavljaju sukladno zakonskim odredbama.\\r\\n\\r\\nVelika pažnja se posvećuje podizanju ekološke svijesti djelatnika i edukaciji o važnosti reciklaže.\\r\\n\\r\\nZračna luka Split u svom budućem djelovanju na zaštiti okoliša planira implementirati sustave obnovljivih izvora energije, te primjeniti suvremene metode i opremu s ciljem kontinuiranog praćenja globalnih trendova u zaštiti okoliša\",\"_bottom_text\":\"field_67ea882efb29a\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->','Zaštita okoliša','','publish','closed','closed','','zastita-okolisa','','','2025-04-17 12:24:58','2025-04-17 12:24:58','',0,'http://localhost/split-airport/?page_id=729',0,'page','',0),(730,1,'2025-04-17 12:19:45','2025-04-17 12:19:45','','sustainability-hero','','inherit','open','closed','','sustainability-hero','','','2025-04-17 12:19:45','2025-04-17 12:19:45','',729,'http://localhost/split-airport/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sustainability-hero.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(731,1,'2025-04-17 12:19:45','2025-04-17 12:19:45','','sustainability-hero','','inherit','open','closed','','sustainability-hero-2','','','2025-04-17 12:19:45','2025-04-17 12:19:45','',0,'http://localhost/split-airport/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sustainability-hero.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(732,1,'2025-04-17 12:19:56','2025-04-17 12:19:56','<!-- wp:acf/block-page-hero {\"name\":\"acf/block-page-hero\",\"data\":{\"background\":730,\"_background\":\"field_67e6ae84b07c8\",\"title\":\"Zaštita okoliša\",\"_title\":\"field_67ea3950a9c62\",\"working_hours\":\"\",\"_working_hours\":\"field_67ee85618587f\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->','Zaštita okoliša','','inherit','closed','closed','','729-revision-v1','','','2025-04-17 12:19:56','2025-04-17 12:19:56','',729,'http://localhost/split-airport/hr/?p=732',0,'revision','',0),(733,1,'2025-04-17 12:20:17','2025-04